trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> class manages a collection of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: La clase <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> administra una colección de objetos <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.#ctor" /> constructor creates an instance of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: El constructor <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.#ctor" /> crea una instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object to add.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> que se agrega.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.Add(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl)" /> method adds a new <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object to the collection.
trans-unit.target: El método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.Add(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl)" /> agrega un nuevo objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> a la colección.

trans-unit.source: The index of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> at which the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object has been added.
trans-unit.target: Índice de <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> en el que se ha agregado el objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="control" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="control" /> es una referencia nula (<see langword="Nothing" /> en Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.AddRange(*)" /> method adds a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> object to the current collection.
trans-unit.target: El método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.AddRange(*)" /> agrega un objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> a la colección actual.

trans-unit.source: An array of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> objects to add to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Matriz de objetos <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> que se agregará a la colección.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.AddRange(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl[])" /> method adds an array of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> objects to the collection.
trans-unit.target: El método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.AddRange(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl[])" /> agrega una matriz de objetos <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> a la colección.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="controls" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="controls" /> es una referencia nula (<see langword="Nothing" /> en Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: A member of the array is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: Un miembro de la matriz es una referencia nula (<see langword="Nothing" /> en Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> object to add to this collection.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> que se va a agregar a esta colección.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.AddRange(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection)" /> method adds a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> object to the current collection.
trans-unit.target: El método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.AddRange(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection)" /> agrega un objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> a la colección actual.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="controlCollection" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="controlCollection" /> es una referencia nula (<see langword="Nothing" /> en Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object for which to search.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> que se va a buscar.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.Contains(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl)" /> method determines whether this <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> object contains a specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object.
trans-unit.target: El método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.Contains(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl)" /> determina si este objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> contiene un objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object is part of the collection; <see langword="false" />, otherwise.
trans-unit.target: Es <see langword="true" /> si el objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> especificado es parte de la colección; en caso contrario, es <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: A one-dimensional array that is the destination of the elements copied from the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Matriz unidimensional que constituye el destino de los elementos copiados desde el objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of <c>array</c> where copying begins.
trans-unit.target: Índice de base cero de <c>array</c> donde se comienza a copiar.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.CopyTo(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl[],System.Int32)" /> method copies the entire collection to a one-dimensional array, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: El método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.CopyTo(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl[],System.Int32)" /> copia toda la colección en una matriz unidimensional, comenzando por el índice especificado de la matriz de destino.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="array" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="array" /> es una referencia nula (<see langword="Nothing" /> en Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is less than zero.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> es menor que cero.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="array" /> is multidimensional
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="array" /> es multidimensional.

trans-unit.source: -or-
trans-unit.target: O bien

trans-unit.source: The number of elements in the source <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> is greater than the available space from <paramref name="index" /> to the end of the destination <paramref name="array" />.
trans-unit.target: El número de elementos de la <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> de origen es mayor que el espacio disponible desde <paramref name="index" /> hasta el final de la <paramref name="array" /> de destino.

trans-unit.source: The type of the source <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> cannot be cast automatically to the type of the destination <paramref name="array" />.
trans-unit.target: El tipo de la <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> de origen no puede convertirse automáticamente al tipo de la <paramref name="array" /> de destino.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object for which the index is returned.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> para el que se devuelve el índice.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.IndexOf(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl)" /> method returns the zero-based index of the first occurrence of the specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object in the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: El método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.IndexOf(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl)" /> devuelve el índice de base cero de la primera aparición del objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> especificado en <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The index value of the specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object, if found; otherwise, -1.
trans-unit.target: Valor de índice del objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> especificado, si se encuentra; en caso contrario, -1.

trans-unit.source: The index in the collection at which to insert the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Índice de la colección donde se va a insertar el objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object to be inserted into the collection.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> que se va a insertar en la colección.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.Insert(System.Int32,System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl)" /> method inserts the specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object into the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: El método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.Insert(System.Int32,System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl)" /> inserta el objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> especificado en la colección <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" />, en el índice especificado.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="value" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="value" /> es una referencia nula (<see langword="Nothing" /> en Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is less than zero, or <paramref name="index" /> is greater than the number of elements in the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> object.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" /> es menor que cero o <paramref name="index" /> es mayor que el número de elementos del objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> is read-only, or <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> has a fixed size.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> es de solo lectura o <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> tiene un tamaño fijo.

trans-unit.source: The index value of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Valor de índice del objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.Item(System.Int32)" /> property contains the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: La propiedad <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.Item(System.Int32)" /> contiene el objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> en el índice especificado.

trans-unit.source: Contains the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: Contiene el objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> en el índice especificado.

trans-unit.source: There was an attempt to set the property to <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: Se ha intentado establecer la propiedad en <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: The object to evaluate.
trans-unit.target: Objeto que se va a evaluar.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.OnValidate(System.Object)" /> method verifies that <paramref name="value" /> is a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object.
trans-unit.target: El método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.OnValidate(System.Object)" /> comprueba que <paramref name="value" /> sea un objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" />.

trans-unit.source: This method does not return a value.
trans-unit.target: Este método no devuelve ningún valor.

trans-unit.source: Instead, an exception is thrown if the specified object is null or is not a valid <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl> object.
trans-unit.target: En su lugar, se produce una excepción si el objeto especificado es null o no es válido <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl> objeto.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="value" /> is a null reference (<see langword="Nothing" /> in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="value" /> es una referencia nula (<see langword="Nothing" /> en Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="value" /> is not a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="value" /> no es un objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object to remove.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> que se quita.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.Remove(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl)" /> method removes the first occurrence of the specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> object from the collection.
trans-unit.target: El método <see cref="M:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection.Remove(System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl)" /> quita la primera aparición del objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> especificado de la colección.

trans-unit.source: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> is read-only, or <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> has a fixed size.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> es de solo lectura o <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControlCollection" /> tiene un tamaño fijo.
